WEBVTT

00:02.921 --> 00:04.756
- So, my dad cleaned out
- our bomb shelter,

00:04.797 --> 00:06.007
And he sent me

00:06.008 --> 00:07.216
my favorite doll.

00:07.258 --> 00:08.384
"Military Mary:

00:08.385 --> 00:09.510
super soldier by day...

