00:17.977 --> 00:19.646
How'd she get that scar?

00:19.647 --> 00:21.313
From a bayonet, or a unicorn?

00:22.356 --> 00:23.792
- I don't know.
- She came with the scar,

00:23.816 --> 00:25.235
And her background

00:25.236 --> 00:26.652
is classified.

00:26.694 --> 00:28.384
You know, Zuri,

00:28.385 --> 00:30.072
I was just about your age

00:26.694 --> 00:30.072
when my dad gave me Mary.

00:30.114 --> 00:31.261
This doll helped

00:31.262 --> 00:32.408
get me through some

00:30.114 --> 00:32.408
pretty tough times.

00:32.450 --> 00:33.743
You mean like back

00:33.744 --> 00:35.035
in India, when I was

00:32.450 --> 00:35.035
bitten by that cobra

00:35.077 --> 00:36.829
and had to walk

00:36.830 --> 00:38.581
five miles to obtain

00:35.077 --> 00:38.581
some used anti-venom?

00:38.623 --> 00:40.959
Uphill?

00:41.000 --> 00:42.106
No, but one time

00:42.107 --> 00:43.210
I had to walk home

00:41.000 --> 00:43.210
from the mall

00:43.252 --> 00:44.921
- 'cause my dad forgot
- to pick me up.

00:44.963 --> 00:46.088
You win.

00:47.966 --> 00:49.488
My point is, Military Mary

00:49.489 --> 00:51.010
is very special to me,

00:51.051 --> 00:52.720
and she deserves

00:52.721 --> 00:54.388
a very special

00:51.051 --> 00:54.388
little girl to play with.

00:54.430 --> 00:56.098
So Zuri,

00:56.140 --> 00:57.329
her new orders

00:57.330 --> 00:58.517
are to bunk with you.

00:59.351 --> 01:02.271
Thank you.

01:02.313 --> 01:04.607
But are you sure

01:04.608 --> 01:06.901
she wouldn't be happier

01:02.313 --> 01:06.901
back in the bomb shelter?

01:06.943 --> 01:08.216
(SCOFFS) This is a

01:08.217 --> 01:09.487
20 million dollar penthouse.

01:09.528 --> 01:10.655
