Found them.

02:15.594 --> 02:17.304
Oh, thanks.

02:17.346 --> 02:18.410
By any chance,

02:18.411 --> 02:19.473
has anyone seen

02:17.346 --> 02:19.473
my nose-hair trimmers?

02:21.308 --> 02:22.601
- Feel free
- to take a look.

02:23.602 --> 02:25.354
Sorry, guys,

02:25.396 --> 02:27.356
- I just can't seem
- to focus these days,

02:27.398 --> 02:29.692
And I feel all woozy inside.

02:29.734 --> 02:30.985
Maybe you're sick.

02:31.027 --> 02:32.945
It's Salma Espinosa.

02:32.987 --> 02:34.030
Is that contagious?

02:34.613 --> 02:36.240
It's not a disease!

02:36.281 --> 02:37.575
It's the name of the most

02:37.576 --> 02:38.868
beautiful woman on earth!

02:38.910 --> 02:40.452
- She's the neighbor's
- personal chef,

02:40.494 --> 02:41.829
And let's just say

02:41.830 --> 02:43.163
she is one hot tamale.

02:44.248 --> 02:45.520
Bertram, we're going

02:45.521 --> 02:46.792
to help you get Salma.

02:46.834 --> 02:49.169
Oh. Absolutely not.

02:49.211 --> 02:51.065
- But aren't you tired
- of spending your nights

02:51.089 --> 02:52.341
Polishing your nesting dolls

02:52.342 --> 02:53.591
with your tears?

02:53.632 --> 02:54.967
Yes.

02:56.719 --> 02:58.075
But there's no way

02:58.076 --> 02:59.430
I'm letting you two meddle

02:56.719 --> 02:59.430
in my personal life.

03:00.222 --> 03:01.348
Okay.

03:03.517 --> 03:05.019
Just so we're clear,

03:05.020 --> 03:06.520
we are going to

03:03.517 --> 03:06.520
meddle, right?

03:06.562 --> 03:08.480
- Like Michael Phelps
- at the Olympics.

03:13.027 --> 03:14.591
Okay, Mary. Your mission

03:14.592 --> 03:16.155
is to scratch my back.

03:17.698 --> 03:19.658
Ah, mission accomplished.

03:20.451 --> 03:21.911
(CELL PHONE RINGING)

03:23.037 --> 03:24.496
Uh, it's Darla.

03:24.538 --> 03:25.748
