03:25.790 --> 03:27.374
- She has unlimited
- bragging minutes.

03:30.377 --> 03:33.005
Darla, hi!

03:33.047 --> 03:35.049
Oh! Oh, you're calling

03:35.050 --> 03:37.051
from your boyfriend's

03:33.047 --> 03:37.051
private submarine?

03:38.136 --> 03:39.553
Lucky you.

03:40.262 --> 03:44.475
Ooh, a Bunny-Bot 3000!

03:44.516 --> 03:46.852
Hey, is that an original

03:46.853 --> 03:49.188
Military Mary doll?

03:49.229 --> 03:51.231
(CHUCKLES)

03:51.232 --> 03:53.233
Simon Sneed is the name,

03:49.229 --> 03:53.233
toy collecting is my game.

03:53.275 --> 03:54.610
As is making rather

03:54.611 --> 03:55.945
obvious rhymes, apparently.

03:57.738 --> 03:58.739
Watch this.

03:59.698 --> 04:01.951
(ELECTRONIC WHIRRING)

04:01.993 --> 04:03.744
- You're the best
- boy or girl ever!

04:03.786 --> 04:05.579
Tell your mommy to buy

04:05.580 --> 04:07.372
my DVDs, backpacks,

04:03.786 --> 04:07.372
and lunch boxes.

04:07.999 --> 04:09.792
And best of all.

04:09.834 --> 04:11.418
Hold out your hands.

04:11.460 --> 04:12.628
(WHIRRING)

04:13.462 --> 04:14.839
(GASPS)

04:14.880 --> 04:16.548
Chocolate poop?

04:18.634 --> 04:19.802
Delicious!

04:21.887 --> 04:23.181
I'll tell you what.

04:23.222 --> 04:24.620
I'll take that old,

04:24.621 --> 04:26.017
scar-faced doll

04:23.222 --> 04:26.017
off your hands

04:26.058 --> 04:27.206
in exchange

04:27.207 --> 04:28.352
for the brand new

04:26.058 --> 04:28.352
Bunny-Bot.

04:28.727 --> 04:29.895
Deal!

04:31.313 --> 04:32.606
BOTH: Sucker!

04:36.318 --> 04:38.362
(CELL PHONE RINGING)

04:38.403 --> 04:40.322
Luke, are you almost here?

04:40.364 --> 04:41.928
Great. Initiating Operation

04:41.929 --> 04:43.492
Beauty and the Butler.

04:43.534 --> 04:45.285
I'm calling her right now.

04:48.747 --> 04:50.457
Salma Espinosa?

04:50.499 --> 04:52.435
- (IN DEEP VOICE) - Yo, this is Tony
- From the lobby.

04:52.459 --> 04:53.544
I need to see youse

04:53.545 --> 04:54.628
down here real quick.

04:54.670 --> 04:55.671
Go Jets!

04:57.548 --> 04:58.632
(ELEVATOR BELL DINGS)

05:01.093 --> 05:03.012
Hola, Bertram.

05:03.595 --> 05:05.014
(STAMMERS)

05:08.976 --> 05:10.437
You know, you two

05:10.438 --> 05:11.896
have a lot in common.

05:11.937 --> 05:12.938
Like cooking,

05:12.939 --> 05:13.939
and...

05:14.773 --> 05:15.900
breathing.

05:17.568 --> 05:18.673
So, have fun

05:18.674 --> 05:19.778
with that. Bye!

05:27.912 --> 05:29.038
(CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY)

05:29.080 --> 05:30.998
(HICCUPS) Oh.

05:31.040 --> 05:32.604
I'm sorry, I always get

05:32.605 --> 05:34.168
hiccups when I'm nervous.

05:34.210 --> 05:35.733
Especially when

05:35.734 --> 05:37.255
I'm around beautiful women.

05:37.296 --> 05:38.381
Oh, you think

05:38.382 --> 05:39.464
I'm beautiful?

05:39.506 --> 05:40.946
You make me turn

05:40.947 --> 05:42.384
as red as the tomatoes

05:39.506 --> 05:42.384
in my paella.

05:43.635 --> 05:45.137
I love paella.

05:45.179 --> 05:46.910
Oh, well... Perhaps we could

05:46.911 --> 05:48.640
cook for each other sometime.

05:48.682 --> 05:50.122
Like this Saturday?

05:50.123 --> 05:51.560
(HICCUPPING CONTINUES)

05:51.602 --> 05:53.062
I should be over

05:53.063 --> 05:54.521
these hiccups by then.

05:54.563 --> 05:56.253
Well, this Saturday

05:56.254 --> 05:57.942
there is a salsa contest

05:54.563 --> 05:57.942
in the park.

05:57.983 --> 05:59.298
(GASPS) We could

05:59.299 --> 06:00.611
enter together...

06:00.652 --> 06:02.301
I love salsa!

06:02.302 --> 06:03.948
I'm the salsa king!

06:03.989 --> 06:06.409
Bueno. Oh, I cannot wait

06:06.410 --> 06:08.827
to salsa the night away.

06:12.164 --> 06:13.332
(HICCUPS)

06:14.666 --> 06:16.168
She meant the salsa

06:16.169 --> 06:17.669
dancing contest!

06:17.711 --> 06:18.730
- What did you
- think she meant?

06:18.754 --> 06:20.505
A salsa making contest!

06:20.547 --> 06:22.237
You know,

06:22.238 --> 06:23.926
diced tomatoes,

06:20.547 --> 06:23.926
onions, cilantro!

06:23.968 --> 06:25.240
Who dances in the park?

06:25.241 --> 06:26.511
That's crazy!

06:26.553 --> 06:27.826
And making salsa

06:27.827 --> 06:29.098
in the park is sane?

06:30.724 --> 06:32.018
You two got me into this,

06:32.019 --> 06:33.311
you're gonna get me out.

06:33.352 --> 06:34.979
You've got three days

06:34.980 --> 06:36.605
to teach me how

06:33.352 --> 06:36.605
to salsa dance.

06:37.982 --> 06:39.004
Is three days

06:39.005 --> 06:40.025
going to be enough?

06:40.067 --> 06:41.903
Only if we can cut down

06:41.904 --> 06:43.737
his nap time to less

06:40.067 --> 06:43.737
than six hours a day.

06:47.658 --> 06:49.139
I cannot believe

06:49.140 --> 06:50.619
you gave Jessie's

06:47.658 --> 06:50.619
doll away.

06:50.661 --> 06:52.830
She will be very upset.

06:52.871 --> 06:54.665
Okay, done with Darla.

06:54.706 --> 06:56.021
The sub went under a whale

06:56.022 --> 06:57.335
so she lost reception.

06:58.919 --> 07:00.442
Then I guess

07:00.443 --> 07:01.964
we're done here.

06:58.919 --> 07:01.964
Better go home.

07:02.006 --> 07:03.632
Wait, wait, wait!

07:03.674 --> 07:05.050
Where's Military Mary?

07:07.678 --> 07:09.430
She shipped out.

07:09.431 --> 07:11.182
She promised to write.

07:11.223 --> 07:12.391
What do you mean,

07:12.392 --> 07:13.558
"shipped out"?

07:13.600 --> 07:15.644
Okay, okay. Fine.

07:15.686 --> 07:17.896
I cannot tell a lie.

07:17.938 --> 07:19.128
Ravi traded her

07:19.129 --> 07:20.316
to a toy dealer.

07:21.525 --> 07:24.569
She can tell a lie!

07:24.611 --> 07:26.697
Zuri traded your

07:26.698 --> 07:28.782
precious memories for

07:24.611 --> 07:28.782
an incontinent varmint!

07:30.492 --> 07:32.077
On the bright side,

07:32.078 --> 07:33.662
I made out like a bandit.

07:33.704 --> 07:35.122
Meet Bunny-Bot.

07:35.831 --> 07:37.708
(ELECTRONIC WHIRRING)

07:40.002 --> 07:41.399
So you traded

07:41.400 --> 07:42.796
Military Mary

07:42.838 --> 07:43.923
for a bunny that

07:43.924 --> 07:45.007
poops chocolate?

07:46.133 --> 07:47.843
- It's Swiss!
- With almonds!

07:55.976 --> 07:57.457
One, two, three.

07:57.458 --> 07:58.937
Five, six, seven.

07:55.976 --> 07:58.937
